{"tid":2279231,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"咁啱得咁橋大快活我都忍撚夠你","createTime":"2020-11-09T15:30:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-11T04:52:08.000Z","uid":152147,"like":45,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"2cc520dec8d04cc8fe08bc13a91a4df99d789855","tid":2279231,"uid":152147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T15:30:26.000Z","msg":"50蚊唔洗 有個類似出面大排檔嘅煲仔飯食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同樣50蚊唔洗 有菠蘿咕嚕肉食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當然味道就比唔上大排檔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鑊氣更加提都唔好提<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但接近一半價錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最重要係十間大排檔有九間都藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n算係咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KWicHxA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKWicHxA.png&h=0db703b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n照翻傳統 <br />\n食左一半先影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後想問九龍東有邊間好食又黃嘅大排檔<br />\n想屌煲仔飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb92fa018dd82c9049502fcf1261c83fd49fd625","tid":2279231,"uid":152147,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T15:31:34.000Z","msg":"Btw佢個飯得兩飯雞翼<br />\n恰鳩me"},{"pid":"e10dfc33cc81af729b43a1ab8c81b408f85c75a0","tid":2279231,"uid":46835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T15:32:15.000Z","msg":"早兩日行過阿活，見佢個煲仔飯外賣只要加$6<br />\n個煲都可以帶埋返屋企<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71469ca4df8655e4624097541bff69754ff30561","tid":2279231,"uid":152147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e10dfc33cc81af729b43a1ab8c81b408f85c75a0","tid":2279231,"uid":46835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy